!! About Pillar 

Pillar is a system to manage documents (e.g. books, presentations, and web sites). From a common model, it is able to generate documents in multiple formats (html, markdown, latex, AsciiDoc). 
It is composed of several modules such as importers, transformers, the document model and outputers.

